{"tid":2436844,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"即派快相冇派到係咪即係冇中?","createTime":"2021-03-07T12:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T06:10:44.000Z","uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"883250dd09ae1d609e4c22199e954566de215d0b","tid":2436844,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"我想問即派快相係咪只會即派?會唔會之後再收信?<br />\n<br />\n因為今早渣車條路冇咩車，好暢通，真係冇留意自己行緊幾多，不過就快過隔離D車既。<br />\n<br />\n之後過咗冇耐就見到鐵馬等緊，但又冇追我，反而再行前D其他鐵馬截左幾部係度抄緊。<br />\n<br />\n所以我就好奇究竟係我根本冇超速，定係好彩唔截即係冇事。"},{"pid":"aa92643f3bb820f526a24e948fec806f80aa36e4","tid":2436844,"uid":140834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d55132ce81e8aeb339e9e9236734100140522a","tid":2436844,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa92643f3bb820f526a24e948fec806f80aa36e4","tid":2436844,"uid":140834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90daa743d612369e05a9b4ca9949d224b9dd4901","tid":2436844,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92d55132ce81e8aeb339e9e9236734100140522a","tid":2436844,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa92643f3bb820f526a24e948fec806f80aa36e4","tid":2436844,"uid":140834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T01:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c0151aa81d0916334c928385f5cf7a1c118db9","ti